keywhiz.generators

Class SecretGenerator<RequestType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • keywhiz.generators.SecretGenerator<RequestType>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TemplatedSecretGenerator

    public abstract class SecretGenerator<RequestType>
extends Object
    A SecretGenerator is used to generate 1 or more of Secrets based on some provided parameters defined on a per-implementation basis. See TemplatedSecretGenerator for an example. See SecretGeneratorsResource to see how this interfaces with the HTTP API.
